000100 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
000200 program-id.    cipher.
000300 
000400 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
000500 
000600 DATA DIVISION.
000700 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
000800
000900 01  str-input       pic x(15) value "John Paul Welsh".
001000 01  chr-shift       pic 99    value 04.
001100 01  max-shift       pic 99    value 26.
001200 01  encrypted       pic x(15).
001300 01  decrypted       pic x(15).
001300 01  chr-count       pic 99    value 0.
001300 01  ascii-val       pic 999.
001400 
001500 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
001600 
001700 program-begin.
001800*    this is a comment
002200     display "The input string is " str-input
002200     display "The shift amount is " chr-shift
002300     display "The max shift amount is " max-shift
002300     
002300     perform 15 times
002300         display chr-count
002300*        increment the counter
002300         add 1, chr-count giving chr-count
002300     end-perform.
002300     
002400 program-done.
002500     stop run.

